column5: Brown's Marine in Elgin OK?Looking to purchase a Princecraft and Has anyone dealt with Browns Marine in Elgin, and if so how was your experience with them?Thanks.
I haven't had any experience with Brown's but I sure like the princecraft's. Just ordered mine last Monday.
You might check out Steele County Marine in Owatonna....507-451-6480.Ask for Mike.. FYISprinter
